<strong>From: JANET PHELAN &lt;<a href="http://mc/compose?to=janetcphelan@yahoo.com" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">janetcphelan@yahoo.com</a>&gt;<br />
Subject: Per our conversation today&#8211;vulnerability to bioterrorism through critical infrastructure<br />
To:</strong><strong> <a href="http://mc/compose?to=nicc@dhs.gov" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">nicc@dhs.gov</a><br />
Date: Friday, August 5, 2011, 3:42 PM</p>
<p></strong></p>
