<p>Larsen&#8217;s response was terse and to the point. On September 8, 2012, he sent me this message from his I phone:</p>
<p><strong>“After reading some of your pieces on the Internet about the Patriot Act, I assure you we will have no further conversations or email exchanges. Sorry I wasted your time and mine.”</strong></p>
<p>Well, at least he has locked in on the Skippy terrorism. What a relief. I was beginning to think we might have a problem</p>
